  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Welsh Secretary Simon Hart and Chief Secretary to the Treasury Stephen Barclay agree funding for coal tip and flood damage remediation work across Wales.</p>

  </div>
</div>

